{"tid":622122,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求解夢👏🏻","createTime":"2018-04-09T01:23:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-09T04:36:56.000Z","uid":17301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3d69c7723061eb23edd7e945efcb98787f8d72e6","tid":622122,"uid":17301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T01:23:11.000Z","msg":"發左個夢好奇怪，求大師幫手解下話我知個夢做乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個夢發生係一個浮空左既類似遺跡咁既地方<br />\n<br />\n個天係全黑既 連月亮都冇<br />\n<br />\n奇怪係我又睇到個環境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n記得我一路行一路有好多黑貓本身訓係度，我一行近就起身望住我<br />\n<br />\n行左一陣但唔知點解我好似若無其事咁完全唔覺得驚<br />\n<br />\n我又好似好眼訓想搵地方訓咁<br />\n<br />\n行到去一個位有隻唔知豹定虎咁既野開口叫我唔好驚，仲話呢邊有位叫我訓佢隔離<br />\n<br />\n然後我又真係若無其事咁訓係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n訓左唔夠一陣feel 到雙手比野禁住，一開眼見到頭先隻豹/虎望住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後佢張開佢個血盤大口想咬落我喉嚨，我成條頸好似已經麻痺曬完全掙扎唔到<br />\n<br />\n之後我就醒左了"},{"pid":"1f478d469aebba05305ce2330b9600ecaed8e0ec","tid":622122,"uid":172840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T01:23:51.000Z","msg":"下世小心d<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66280c73c24b51349dfe08010ebd305b8559c21f","tid":622122,"uid":17301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f478d469aebba05305ce2330b9600ecaed8e0ec","tid":622122,"uid":172840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T01:23:51.000Z","msg":"下世小心d<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T01:30:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1671043fdebcd5a6ff3e1dc1509050492c84cb9","tid":622122,"uid":127033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T03:08:03.000Z","msg":"小心啲 血光之災"},{"pid":"df6a78a73836431a8091e50297d1fc4dc279a1fd","tid":622122,"uid":17301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T04:36:56.000Z","msg":"個夢愈諗愈唔對路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲要咁多隻黑貓"}]}